column4: Q1 Q1: First I would like to ask you about your current situation / family situation. How would you rate it on a scale from 1 to 5?
Q22 Q22: How would you describe the situation of your family since the beginning of the war in March 2015?

column6: We are doing fine and are not affected by the war
column8: Life has become a little bit more difficult, but we are doing fine
column10: We are suffering a little bit from the increase of prices for food, medicine and fuel
column12: We are suffering a lot from the increase of prices for food, medicine and fuel
column14: We are not able to buy food, medicine and fuel
